{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_FireSkullRodPL2}}
'''A_FireSkullRodPL2'''<br>
(''no parameter'')<br>

Fires a {{Class|HornRodFX2}} and makes it play the sound "weapons/hornrodpowshoot" on the WEAPON channel. If the player has a possible target right ahead, it is put in the projectile's <tt>tracer</tt> field.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|SkullRodPowered}} and derived classes.

